sub_title: who is looking for something new
summary:
喜爱心理学、有思辨和批判精神的中文老师，儿童观是“孩子是一个独立的人”。
会说普通话、广东话、英语、荷兰语。坚持不懈、执行力强。
喜欢学习新技能、尝试新鲜事物，兴趣是画画和音乐。
A Chinese teacher who loves psychology, is thoughtful and critical, and her view on children is that "a child is an independent person."
She can speak Mandarin, Cantonese, English, Dutch. Perseverance and strong execution.
She likes to learn new skills and try new things. Her hobby is painting and music.
Chunyansongwork@gmail.com
